messages.text: What? I can’t talk right now.
Haha. Seriously. Who is this? Blake?
Ok. Well, lame joke. I have to go back to my test.
I’m going to turn my phone off.
Do u want me to tell?
We’re not supposed to have our phones out during the test.
You’ve gotten away with way more. :).
I just want you to do what’s right.
I know you found the answers to the mid-term.
And you went and copied them with Ainsley.
And you left Phoebe as your lookout.
What do u suppose would happen if the principal found out? :).
What did u get on the midterm?
But not proof. I took Philosophy and Law.
But you’re the valedictorian. You’re held to a higher standard.
U don’t know that for sure.
The class GPA’S are listed in the hall.
Heather who’s never cheated on a test.
But Heather works hard. She doesn’t always get 100’s.
Stop talking in the third person.
Fine. I work hard. And I don’t deserve to be cheated.
So that’s what this is all about? U want to be valedictorian???
It’s not my fault Mr. Harper can’t teach.
He barely understands the material himself.
If I had a better teacher I wouldn’t have to cheat.
Maybe the smartest person is the person who knows how to work the system.
And u know all about that, don’t u?
Ur parent’s paid a lot of money for u to get into St. Geneivive’s.
No. I got in on merit.
Heather got in on merit. U got in for a new auditorium.
And now you’re going to be valedictorian and then go to Berkeley.
What do u think would happen if Berkeley found out about ur cheating?
Phoebe is a nice girl. But she talks too much.
Get her talking and who knows what she’ll say.
I have to finish my test!
No, you’re going to fail it.
Fail it and I won’t go to the principal.
Don’t talk to me about fairness. U cheated!
Heather doesn’t have her phone out.
I told you not to look.
R u trying to bring us both down???
Ainsley just turned in her test.
U know, the lookout didn’t actually steal the test or make the copies.
Probably just get a slap on the wrist.
Ur not even in the top ten in GPA!
Stupid Phoebe. Not even in the top ten.
You’ve always kept me out of the inner circle, Bridgette.
I’m putting in the wrong answers…
Would u like to know who I am?
I knew you cheated when you all got 100’s.
I figured Phoebe was the look-out.
With a failing final exam you can be assured you won’t be valedictorian.
Prestigious schools like Berkeley don’t like to see their newly admitted students slipping at the end of the year…
I bet they’d like to know about this test.
Try to look on the bright side, Bridgette.
It looks like I taught you something after all.
